      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Sept 27 obituary about Lawrence G Hauck, former news editor of The New York Times; his military service noted, as well as daughter's name</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary on Sept. 27 about Lawrence G. Hauck, a former news editor of The New York Times, referred incorrectly to his military service and omitted a survivor. Mr. Hauck served in air combat intelligence with the Navy in World War II; he was not a pilot. His sole immediate survivor is a daughter, Linda Lamb of Manhattan.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
